The thing that worries me more than anything else is a guy like bin laden who doesnt want hundreds of nukes, he only needs 1 at a time. </TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#FFFFFF>*</td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><font class="bfont"><B>The Judge™</B></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><font class="bfont">Sorry...this will clarify.<br />
