Is it just me or does anyone else get the impression of George Bush that he is a 6 year old with a bucket full of army men, a bathtub full of ships and subs, and a box full of rockets? He has more than all his little friends in the neighborhood and just cant wait to show them off?? </TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#CCCCCC>*</td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#CCCCCC><font class="bfont"><B>Old Gaffer™</B></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor=#CCCCCC><font class="bfont">I think this was a general comment about a very specific circumstance, but the powers that be couldn&#39;t be specific in making the statement.  I read the whole thing as <br />
