"Saddam, if you use any nasty crap on Israel, Turkey, Iran (yes even Iran who Saddam also hates), or anybody else, we will drop the same on you, only more of it."  <br />
<br />
On the other hand, if India were to nuke Pakistan, I don&#39;t think we&#39;d have the balls to blow away a couple million Hindus.  And if China were to nuke Tawain, no way in hell would go near that one.  So I think we&#39;re only talking about the little guy that we could easily beat up.  I&#39;m ok with that because we should have taken him out the last time. </TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#FFFFFF>*</td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><font class="bfont"><B>Serpent™</B></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><font class="bfont">I remember that crap from elementary school.  It usually ended up with me and a friend hitting each other over and over to attempt to get &#39;even&#39;.  We both usually ended with black eyes and detention :P </TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#CCCCCC>*</td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#CCCCCC><font class="bfont"><B>Max of Tat™</B></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor=#CCCCCC><font class="bfont">Sounds like political jargon to me. "If you hit me, I&#39;ll hit you harder." I agree with Mel that HOPEFULLY it doesn&#39;t go any further than that. </TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#FFFFFF>*</td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><font class="bfont"><B>the-mental-1™</B></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><font class="bfont">well it&#39;s the classic stance of "we need these weapons so that ppl don&#39;t use there&#39;s against us in case we retalliate in kind" I think it&#39;s ok if it&#39;s just used like that in a kinda bluff thing but if they actually did use them to retalliate that&#39;s just too scary to think about.  It could *very* easily get out of hand.  I mean ieasterlingroup of terrorists who happen to be in a country with nuclear capability use weapons of mass destruction in a terrorist campaign in your country (or allied countries, or just anywhere in the world) are you going to nuke the terrorists???  I doubt the country they&#39;re in would like that very much at all...<br />
